K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:32b-1: a'arya ru tsi ra aangga yashthi n'a ma dh'a ra n'i /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:32b-3: 'phags pa lus kyi dbyibs mdzes pa zhes bya ba'i gzungs /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:32b-5: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:32b-6: na mo bi pu la bi ma na su pra tishthi te aa sam khe ya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:32b-7: s'urya sha tsha sa ta sra a ti re ka te dza /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:32b-8: pra bh'a aa ba bha si ta murta ye /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:32b-9: ma h'a ma ni mu ku tra kunda la /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:32b-10: aa lam k'a ra dha ri ne bha ga b'a te padma p'a na ye /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:32b-11: sarba lo ka aa ba ya sha ma n'a ya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:32b-12: bi bi dha khu kha sa ma b'a sha aa bishthi /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33a-0: sarba satva pa ri mo tsa k'a @33a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33a-3: ma h'a aa lo ka ka ra na ta ma sti mi ra pa ta la bi n'a sha ka /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33a-4: r'a ga dve sha ma h'a mo ha dzva la sha ma ka /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33a-6: sarba aa pa ya durga ti pra sha ma ka /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33a-7: sarba satva sa m'a shv'a sa na ka ra /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33a-8: sarba a'a sh'a pa ri p'u ra ka /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33a-9: sarba ta th'a ga t'a sam bha na ka ra /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33a-10: he he ma h'a bo dhi satva /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33a-11: ba ra ba ra da ya k'a /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33a-12: padma aa lo ka sam bha ta /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33a-13: ma h'a ka ru ni ka /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33a-15: aa lam kri te shi ra /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33a-16: ma ni ka na ka r'a dza /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33a-17: sha ta badzre bee d'urya aa lam kri ta sh'a r'i ra /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33a-18: aa mi [?] dzi na ka ma la ya a lam kri ta /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33a-19: pra bha ra na r'a dz'a na sha ta sa ha sra a'a bhi la shi ti k'a ya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33a-20: ma h'a bo dhi satva ba ra bi dha ma bi dha ma /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33a-23: ma h'a y'am tra kle sha ka ba t'a aa ba baddha bi bo dhi satva sam sa ra tsa ra ka pra ma th'a na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33a-26: pu ru sha s'a ga ra /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33a-30: su danta pa ri bri ta /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33a-34: pra sh'a sa ya pra sh'a sa ya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33a-35: pra dha na sa ya pra dha na sa ya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33a-38: bi dhi ri bi dhi ri /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33a-40: bi bi ri bi bi ri /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33a-48: bi dhu na bi dhu na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33a-51: g'a dha ya g'a dha ya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33b-0: @33b pra ha sa pra ha sa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33b-1: n'a n'a bi bi dha kle sha pa sa n'a /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33b-3: sam ha ra sam ha ra /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33b-4: dhu ru ti dhu ru ti /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33b-5: ma h'a manda aa la k'a ra na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33b-7: aa ba bhi si t'a ma h'a bi sha sha ma ka; ma h'a bo dhi satva pa ra da sv'a h'a /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33b-8: bcom ldan 'das lag na padma'i lus kyi dbyibs mdzes pa zhes bya ba'i gzungs byang chub sems dpa'i khang bzang dam pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33b-9: rdo rje chen pos bgegs par gsungs pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33b-14: lha ma yin chen pos bstod pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33b-15: re ba thams cad phun sum tshogs par byed pa 'di sgrib pa chen po mang pos bsgribs pa gang la la zhig nyan tam /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33b-19: mthong nas legs par rtogs par byed na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33b-20: de'i las dang nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa thams cad yongs su byang bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33b-21: nang par langs nas lan gcig bton na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33b-22: lag na padma phyi bzhin 'brang bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33b-23: yid la gang dag 'dod pa'i dgos pa bsam pa tsam gyis 'grub par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33b-24: gcig pu rab tu dben par 'dug ste sangs rgyas yid la bya ba mngon du dmigs nas bcom ldan 'das lag na padma rjes su dran par byas la lan bdun brjod na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:33b-25: dam pa ci 'dod pa thob par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:34a-0: @34a *// sems can thams cad kyi yid du 'ong bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:34a-1: de'i ngan 'gro thams cad 'gag par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:34a-2: yud tsam zhig 'chag cing 'dug la yid la brjod na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:34a-3: bskal pa bye ba 'bum phrag du mar bsags pa'i las byang bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:34a-4: 'khor los bsgyur ba stong gis bsags pa'i bsod nams kyi phung po chen po dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:34a-5: tshe rabs tshe rabs su yang padma'i rigs chen por skye bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:34a-6: skye bo khyad par du 'phags pas bkur bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:34a-7: me tog dri zhim pos snyim pa bkang ste 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gi mdun du lan bdun brjod na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:34a-8: yon tan chen po stong thob par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:34a-9: snying rje chen po'i chos nyid snang ba yang de la skye bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:34a-10: dam pa chen po dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:34a-11: de nyid kyi gdong du bltas te bzlas brjod byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:34a-12: bcom ldan 'das zhal rtag tu bzhad pa 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug mthong bar 'gyur zhing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:34a-13: chos snang ba'i gsal ba dang po dri ma med par byed pa zhes bya ba 'thob par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:34a-14: tshe 'di nyid la sangs rgyas rjes su dran pa thob par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:34b-0: sems @34b mnyam par bzhag bzhin du 'chi ba'i dus byed par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:34b-1: tshe rabs thams cad du tshe rabs dran par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:34b-2: ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin du las kyi sgrib pa thams cad zad par byed par 'dod na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:34b-3: tshes bco lnga'i zla ba nya ba la smyung ba byas la gos dkar po bgos te ring bsrel dang bcas pa'i mchod rten nam /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:34b-4: sku gzugs kyi spyan sngar tsandan dkar pos dkyil 'khor bskus la /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:34b-6: bcom ldan 'das la me tog sna tshogs gtor te bcom ldan 'das dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:34b-7: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug la dri zhim po'i bdug pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:34b-9: spos kyis bsti stang byas te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:34b-10: de nyid du 'dug la lan brgya rtsa brgyad brjod na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:34b-11: des sdig pa thams cad dang bral bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:34b-12: mtshams med pa byed pa yang sdig pa byang zhing shin tu yongs su dag pa'i sems kyi rgyud dang ldan pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:34b-13: shin tu yongs su dag pa'i lus dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:34b-15: yid kyi spyod pa dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:34b-16: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyis rtag par rgyun du ting nge 'dzin gyi stobs dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:34b-18: sa dang pha rol tu phyin pa'i stobs dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:34b-19: ye shes khyad par can gyi stobs sgrub par mdzad do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:35a-1: du bltas te bzlas brjod byas na char 'bab bo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:35a-2: sa la bltas te bzlas brjod byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:35a-3: lo tog thams cad legs par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:35a-6: rdzing bu'i shul du bltas te bzlas brjod byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:35a-8: nad thams cad la lag pas bya ba cing bzlas brjod byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:35a-10: dran pa nyams pa'i mdun du bzlas brjod byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:35a-13: skom pa'i gdong du bltas te bzlas brjod byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:35a-15: mi ngas chen po byung na ras la bris te rgyal mtshan gyi rtse mor btags na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:35a-16: dpag tshad tshun chad mtshams gcad pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:35a-18: 'phags pa lus kyi dbyibs mdzes zhes bya ba'i gzungs rdzogs so ////
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:35a-19: rgya gar gyi mkhan po pra dzny'a warma dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-092-008:35a-20: zhu chen gyi lotstsha ba bandhe ye shes sdes bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa /
